description: DataRadioBearer: Table containing radio bearer configuration parameters for data sessions at specific cells.  Columns: dateTime (timestamp of record), Area_Name (geographic area), CellId (unique cell identifier), Id2 (secondary cell identifier), Id3 (additional identifier), Id4 (further identifier), vsDataType (data type identifier), vsDataFormatVersion (data format version), DataRadioBearer.dataRadioBearerId (unique bearer ID), DataRadioBearer.dlPollPdu (downlink polling PDU size), DataRadioBearer.tStatusProhibitDl (downlink status prohibit timer), DataRadioBearer.tStatusProhibitUl (uplink status prohibit timer), DataRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitUl (uplink polling retransmission timer), DataRadioBearer.dlMaxRetxThreshold (downlink maximum retransmission threshold), DataRadioBearer.tPollRetransmitDl (downlink polling retransmission timer), DataRadioBearer.ulMaxRetxThreshold (uplink maximum retransmission threshold), DataRadioBearer.ulPollPdu (uplink polling PDU size).
